opaque

  -- Validity of equality preservation for Π and Σ, seen as type
  -- formers.

  ΠΣ-congᵛ :
    ΠΣ-allowed b p q →
    Γ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ A₁ ≡ A₂ →
    Γ ∙ A₁ ⊩ᵛ⟨ l ⟩ B₁ ≡ B₂ →
